	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001219_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p><placeName>18 Hart St</placeName></p>
<lb/><p>11<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">th</hi></hi> Feby 
<lb/>1858 </p>
<lb/><p>My Dear Shaw</p>
<lb/><p>I was but 
<lb/>once at the 
<lb/>Society<reg>'</reg>s house 
<lb/>and found 
<lb/>you were 
<lb/>engaged with 
<lb/>some people 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001219_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'--> 
<lb/>in the library<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I had nothing 
<lb/>to say. <persName>Sir</persName>
<lb/>Roderick asked 
<lb/>me to meet 
<lb/>him and I 
<lb/>did so and walked 
<lb/>to the end of 
<lb/>the street with 
<lb/>him then went 
<lb/>to the Foreign 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001219_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'--> 
<lb/>Office where 
<lb/>I was detained 
<lb/>till past three 
<lb/>and having 
<lb/>another engagement 
<lb/>at two! I hurried 
<lb/>up and for two reasons 
<lb/>did not call 
<lb/>again. 1<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">st</hi></hi> I 
<lb/>had nothing to 
<lb/>say and did <supplied resp="#SM">not</supplied>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001219_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'--> 
<lb/>wish to disturb 
<lb/>you for nothing<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>2<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">d</hi></hi> I had an 
<lb/>engagement up 
<lb/>here &amp; was more 
<lb/>than 1/2 an 
<lb/>hour behind 
<lb/>my time. I think 
<lb/><persName>Wyon</persName> has got 
<lb/>on well. </p>
<lb/><p>I am &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
			
